My Repository

This is a repository of apps to be used with F-Droid. Applications in this repository are official binaries built by the original application developers and released on the official github pages.

Currently it serves 2 apps. To add it to your F-Droid client, scan the QR code (click it to enlarge) or use this URL:

https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cesaryuan/f-droid-repo-template/main/fdroid/repo
